Title: How Many??
Description:
<Agrikus is crying as you approach.>

They did it... I cannot believe they did it...

Someone has come here and asked for the delivery of ONE THOUSAND herbs!

I cannot even fathom this! It is preposterous. Ridiculous! Ludicrous!!

...Please help.
ObjectivesText: Gather 20 Hochenblume for Agrikus in Valdrakken.
